Frequently Asked Questions about Tricalcium Citrate Anhydrous Market
1. What is tricalcium citrate anhydrous?
Tricalcium citrate anhydrous is a calcium salt of citric acid used as a food additive and dietary supplement.

2. What are the key applications of tricalcium citrate anhydrous?
Tricalcium citrate anhydrous is commonly used in food and beverage products, as well as in pharmaceuticals and dietary supplements.

